cbf","tid":2398300,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T08:55:36.000Z","msg":"外界先前傳出Clubhouse背後的技術是來自於中國科技公司「聲網」（Agora），也就是說假如中國政府有需要，聲網就必須交出使用者個資，對於這起傳聞Clubhouse和聲網都沒有回應。"},{"pid":"87a1bc6448e8ff77b68238eaa2bf03f6fd130b99","tid":2398300,"uid":148355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T11:01:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/technology/熱潮背後-新社交平台-clubhouse-爆紅-聲音通訊技術來自中資公司/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ftechnology%2F%E7%86%B1%E6%BD%AE%E8%83%8C%E5%BE%8C-%E6%96%B0%E7%A4%BE%E4%BA%A4%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0-clubhouse-%E7%88%86%E7%B4%85-%E8%81%B2%E9%9F%B3%E9%80%9A%E8%A8%8A%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E4%BE%86%E8%87%AA%E4%B8%AD%E8%B3%87%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%2F&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOUbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=e847e052\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ftechnology%2F%E7%86%B1%E6%BD%AE%E8%83%8C%E5%BE%8C-%E6%96%B0%E7%A4%BE%E4%BA%A4%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0-clubhouse-%E7%88%86%E7%B4%85-%E8%81%B2%E9%9F%B3%E9%80%9A%E8%A8%8A%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E4%BE%86%E8%87%AA%E4%B8%AD%E8%B3%87%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%2F&h=58626c12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/technology/熱潮背後-新社交平台-clubhouse-爆紅-聲音通訊技術來自中資公司/</a>"},{"pid":"48b56339d2791a1ca0fbd8e868e1a28863b8ec46","tid":2398300,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebd82f6d301072272e4ff74fa035790f54325246","tid":2398300,"uid":375135,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"098793538c6252cadd0837afd85b8e3361ac354d","tid":2398300,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T07:30:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">中國用戶湧入Clubhouse躲避審查 討論新疆、台獨、香港議題</span></strong><br />\n   <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/02/07/phpJiXxzK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F02%2F07%2FphpJiXxzK.jpg&h=030bcddb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國新興語音社群平台Clubhouse大規模湧入逃避言論審查的中國網友，上面「中文房」討論的議題包括新疆集中營、台獨、香港國安法等等。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n2021/02/07 14:51<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國新興語音社群平台Clubhouse，在特斯拉執行長馬斯克（Elon Musk）也投入使用後在全球爆紅，<span class=\"red\">而中國用戶為了避免被當局言論審查，出現大規模湧入Clubhouse的現象，上面「中文房」討論的議題包括新疆集中營、台獨、香港國安法等等。</span><br />\n<br />\n據《路透》報導，中國禁止使用臉書、推特和YouTube等西方社群媒體APP，而且嚴格監控網路避免出現有損共產黨威嚴的言論。至於尚未受到中共當局審查的Clubhouse，只能在iOS設備上使用，而且在中國的App Store無法下載，<span class=\"red\">不過中國用戶自己找到出路，他們透過更改App Store的位置來取得Clubhouse。</span><br />\n<br />\n《路透》查訪了許多中文房，<span class=\"red\">在其中發現有個圍繞香港政治議題的房間，裡面有民運份子、記者和藝術家討論了香港支持美國前總統川普的相關狀況，另外還有中文房聚集了中國、台灣和香港的網友進行交流。</span><br />\n<br />\nClubhouse只能透過現有會員的邀請進入聊天房，<span class=\"red\">目前在中國網拍上邀請碼的售價在50至400人民幣（約新台幣216元至1730元）之間</span>，尚不清楚為何中共政府讓Clubhouse持續在中國境內發展。<br />\n<br />\n不過，外界先前傳出Clubhouse背後的技術是來自於中國科技公司「聲網」（Agora），也就是說假如中國政府有需要，聲網就必須交出使用者個資，對於這起傳聞Clubhouse和聲網都沒有回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3435086\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3435086&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOUbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=eb63af61\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3435086&h=7d1f33e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3435086</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T08:11:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咩係Clubhouse <br />\n咩係快手<br />\n<br />\n全部都黎得太快跟唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T11:28:17.000Z","msg":"快手就好撚耐...Clubhouse就上年已經有 呢排hit左好多"},{"pid":"1159b94d998cb8e2721d1bf710bb1a9f028c60dd","tid":2398300,"uid":375135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48b56339d2791a1ca0fbd8e868e1a28863b8ec46","tid":2398300,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebd82f6d301072272e4ff74fa035790f54325246","tid":2398300,